square_1-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Oasis_contact_square_1-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲乐队</a>已经确认了乐队明年 9 月在温布利球场额外举行的两场演出的私人投票细节。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="507" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-line-up-band-members-guide-3788552"><b>支持我：2025年绿洲阵容中所有可能的球员</b></a></li></ul><p>在英伦流行音乐巨头<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">宣布于八月底回归</a>并确认明年夏天在英国和爱尔兰举办一系列大型演出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-2025-tickets-for-all-dates-sell-out-after-huge-demand-3789311">第一天最初日期的门票就售罄了</a>。</p><p>对于许多粉丝来说，抢到门票的经历充满压力， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">人们排着长队等待几个小时</a>，而其他人则 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">受到与动态定价相关的价格上涨的打击</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3790558" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3790558" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3790558" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR.jpg" alt="Oasis 重聚，开启 2025 年巡演。图片来源：西蒙·埃米特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/OASIS_REUNION_COLOUR-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3790558" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis 重聚，开启 2025 年巡演。图片来源：西蒙·埃米特</figcaption></figure><p>为了回应争议，绿洲周三（9 月 4 日）宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-wembley-stadium-extra-reunion-dates-tickets-invite-only-no-surge-pricing-3790552">他们将在温布利加演两场演出，但这一次对门票销售制定了更严格的规定</a>。</p><p>该乐队为 9 月 27 日星期五和 9 月 28 日星期六在温布利举行的两场新演出采取了“仅限受邀者的特别门票销售策略”，“为弥补这一情况迈出了一小步”。</p><p>现在，绿洲分享了有关投票如何进行的更多细节。他们在社交媒体上的一篇帖子中表示：“参加私人投票的邀请将于今晚（周六）连夜发送给我们能够识别的符合条件的粉丝。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_oOv1EtxlT/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50p