兼演员坦诚地讲述了自己的心理健康问题，并在 2022 年的纪录片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-first-teaser-for-selena-gomez-documentary-my-mind-and-me-3314883"><em>My Mind &amp; Me》</em></a>中详细描述了她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-on-being-diagnosed-with-bipolar-disorder-it-took-the-fear-away-2640849">对双相情感障碍的诊断</a><em>。</em></p><p> <em>“</em>有很多人比我更关心我自己，他们真的希望我做一些我还没有准备好的事情。我必须跌入谷底，我必须在我的时间里做到这一点，”她在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行的 SXSW 小组会议上说道。</p><p>她补充道：“我想并希望我现在处于一个更好的位置。”</p><p>今年早些时候，戈麦斯因在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/only-murders-in-the-building">《大楼里的谋杀案》</a></em>最后一季中的表演而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/fans-react-as-selena-gomez-earns-her-long-overdue-first-emmy-nomination-for-acting-3776151">首次获得艾美奖提名</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-is-reportedly-now-a-billionaire-3791610">据报道，赛琳娜·戈麦斯 (Selena Gomez) 现已成为亿万富翁的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
歌曲作者兼长期钢琴家《Screamin' Scott Simon》去世，享年 75 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/songwriter-and-longtime-sha-na-na-pianist-screamin-scott-simon-has-died-ged-75-3791604?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=作曲家兼长期钢琴家尖叫斯科特西蒙已去世，享年 75 岁Laura MolloySat, 07 Sep 2024 10:57:39 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rock https://www.nme.com/?p=3791604 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尖叫斯科特·西蒙。图片来源：大卫·利文斯顿/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Simon 与 doo-wop 乐队一起表演了 50 多年</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/songwriter-and-longtime-sha-na-na-pianist-screamin-scott-simon-has-died-aged-75-3791604">歌曲作者兼长期钢琴家 Screamin&#39; Scott Simon 去世，享年 75 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="尖叫斯科特·西蒙。图片来源：大卫·利文斯顿/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screamin-Scott-Simon.-CREDIT_-David-Livingston_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Screamin&#39; Scott Simon 是摇滚乐和杜沃普乐队 Sha Na Na 的钢琴家，已有 50 多年的历史，他因鼻窦癌去世，享年 75 岁。</p><p>西蒙于周四（9 月 5 日）去世。他的女儿、作家尼娜·西蒙 (Nina Simon) 宣布了这一消息，她在 Instagram 上写道：“我的父亲是一位摇滚明星。字面上地。沙娜娜成员已有50多年。他喜欢清晨的食客和深夜的舞台。但他最爱的是他的女儿们。”</p><p>她继续说道：“亲爱的丈夫、父亲和祖父（Boppa）。歌手，香蕉蓝莓煎饼的翻转者。有趣且带来欢乐的人。读者和思想家。粉色瑜伽裤穿着者、班卓琴拾音者、kayfabe 知识分子、布吉伍吉钢琴王。孟施。</p><p> “博帕经常说，生活的秘诀就是旅游管理。当他准备最后一次巡演时，我非常感激能和他在一起。虽然为时过早，但一如既往，他准时参加了大型演出。我永远爱你。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_jRdSYS3FU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #